Hitachi SMT Parts HITACHI 0402 nozzle Specs:

1.GXH-1 Modular Mounter – A placement system with the unparalleled placement rate of 80k CPH, and flexibility to place components ranging from 0201 (0603mm) chip to 100 x 26 mm connector.

2. An option exists for the placement of 01005 (0402 mm) chip components. Four placement heads have up to 12 nozzles each & on-the-fly recognition of all components.

3.GXH-3 Modular Mounter – A placement system with the ludicrous placement rate of 95k CPH, and flexibility to place components ranging from 0201 (0603 mm) chip to 100 x 26 mm connector.
